Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what, I'll always be your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.47,0:00:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The car the three of us are riding in...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:07.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is rigged to explode if we lower our speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.89,0:00:08.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.31,0:00:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recognizing that single truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.31,0:00:14.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.89,0:01:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those mountains where...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.11,0:02:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I once ran after hares
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:07.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those streams where...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:11.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I often fished for little fish
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.04,0:02:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many more kilometers until we get to the onsen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still about 100 kilometers I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? We've only traveled for 10 so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.26,0:02:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you keep asking every five minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine to be excited about it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.72,0:02:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be paying attention to our speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.43,0:02:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But today's going to be a great day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:39.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First is the onsen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then a delicious meal, and some good liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'll enjoy it even more since it's half price!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Put me through to Inspector Megure, with the\NMetropolitan Police Investigations Division 1, Section 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, get that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:10.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the Takaoka road.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:17.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm in a car right now with my dad and Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.94,0:03:21.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Takaoka road?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their current location is on the Takaoka road!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:27.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd the inspector say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen up, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.28,0:03:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remain calm and listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That car...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one you're in...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:40.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an explosive device wired to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An explosive device?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:45.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:48.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That car you're in...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you go farther than 10 kilometers,\Nthe explosive device will switch on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,10 kilometers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:03.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means, the switch is already...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:06.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That car...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:08.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do not stop that car!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have to keep moving forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the same time that your speed falls below 20km/h (12.5mph)...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:17.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that's how the criminal wired it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Inspector, couldn't this be a prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit claimed he would blow up the water tower first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since we can't confirm if the threat is true or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's best to assume that there's a real explosive device attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:56.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it exploded just as Uncle happened to pass it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:05.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bomb must have been equipped with a timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was done to prove this wasn't a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A demonstration.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit has a bomb placed in this car...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:34.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just drive calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've engaged emergency measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:44.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:04.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll try to catch up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:10.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regarding the culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll tell you on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:17.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earlier, a man called me, giving the name Sugiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While that's likely an alias...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:22.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that the car Mouri Kogorou\Nrented from Beika Rent-A-Car...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had been fitted with an explosive device.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does someone named "Sugiyama" bring anything to mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugiyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:36.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The clerk from the rental service was named Sugiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:43.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the one who referred us\Nto that half-priced onsen deal today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So long as he could kill a famous detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:50.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he'd become famous as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a joke initially, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He knew about your plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:57.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after seeing the water tower explode...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:07:00.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have no choice but to follow his instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instructions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugiyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wants you to get on the expressway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:07.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The expressway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until we have a better grasp of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's follow his instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:18.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal called, and requested us\Nby name to get on the expressway...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could his choosing today have some special significance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The expressway exit to Takaoka is now closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:38.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The east intersection of the expressway\Ntoward Takaoka is now closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All lanes on the Takaoka road are now closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lane 8 entering Takaoka, as well as\Nthe adjacent road, are now closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:54.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All pedestrian walkways are now closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All road closures confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The roundabout that heads into the\Nexpressway is ready for approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're already coming up on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep your car in the open lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:24.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The inspector is already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police will help however they can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:31.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri Kogorou...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Writhe in terror!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll enjoy it, ever so slowly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:39.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:48.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The gasoline...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:52.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's half gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:55.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I got the car...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was full!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:08:58.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it was fine when we first checked, it must\Nhave started leaking just before we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:04.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before we run out of gasoline...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:08.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get the two of you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:11.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, let the two of them out first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Open the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:15.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:19.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same with the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, what about your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This side's no good either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:26.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:28.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must have been tampered with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only half a tank of gasoline left...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 20 km/h, we have one more hour at most...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When there's no gasoline left, the car will stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.74,0:09:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the windows and doors won't open from the inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megure here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:52.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:57.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure, sorry for the delay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:08.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're depending on you, Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maintain this distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:16.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:20.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get back from the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:36.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While Ran and I can get out once the window glass is broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What will Uncle do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll have to take his foot off the accelerator to get out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which will cause the car to slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:48.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:53.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't let the car go below 20km/h.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will anything work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:00.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move the car back just a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tires?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:05.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tires...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Replace...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tires!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We stop but keep those going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:16.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:23.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's the only way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:25.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:26.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:29.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi, hurry up and save me! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:31.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just hold on, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:32.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:34.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to pull you over now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:45.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:55.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:56.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.05,0:12:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They rescued one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In another ten minutes the gasoline will be all used up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when it will be Mouri's time to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is safe and sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:22.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, we'll get Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:23.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:25.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:28.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're only a few kilometers from the traffic jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's enough space for one car to make it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No more than that, even side-by-side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.07,0:12:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Abort the rescue efforts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:37.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let get on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:45.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:46.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:12:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:13:00.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:02.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:03.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:05.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Kogorou, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:46.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:50.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take my jacket and put it over your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roll after you jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may get hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:56.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:13:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what about you, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saving you comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just do this, for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:13.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Almost there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're almost there, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.43,0:14:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsumiya Ichirou?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a case that we worked to ether.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:31.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit murdered his ex-lover...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, to avoid arrest...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:35.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drove his bike onto the expressway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.53,0:14:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He crashed into the safety railing and died...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three years ago today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I thought that was suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsumiya had a brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time, he was studying in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:52.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't know the circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:56.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how much we explained, he\Nwouldn't believe it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:57.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:14:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why this is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:03.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now, we're looking for his brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll arrest him as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How much gasoline is left?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:12.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:15.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know how long we have...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:20.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:22.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I was a bad father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.91,0:15:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:27.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:40.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri Kogorou...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost time to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:56.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This tunnel... Will become your grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:49.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got Mouri Kogorou...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've avenged you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, if I may ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:10.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Megure, with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsumiya Jirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.69,0:17:19.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something three years ago today...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:21.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Mouri Kogorou was part of...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We looked into cases like that\Nhaving to do with the expressway...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we found your brother, Matsumiya Ichirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:30.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that he had a brother, Matsumiya Jirou...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:33.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how we got to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:35.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:42.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We suspect you used the computer in your house today\Nto hack into the highway department's security.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:45.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, we suspect it's somehow related to our case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you mind coming with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:54.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:55.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugiyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No---- Matsumiya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.19,0:18:00.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look like you just saw a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:03.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How are you still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I simply utilized the clues you left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the car stopped, it should've exploded...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.58,0:18:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the car's gasoline was refueled, it can keep on running.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time until the bomb is disarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wired it to the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.01,0:18:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be disarmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The car kept moving without stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The experts are disarming it as we speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While keeping the speed at 20 km/h.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, when...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:18:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.29,0:19:00.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the tunnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A large truck and an expert bomb squad were waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.81,0:19:17.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They set up a ramp and safety net...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:20.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All set!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All I had to do was drive the car onto the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:38.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once the car made it onto the truck bed, the net stopped it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:41.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While tire rollers kept the tires spinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, they were able to move in and rescue Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.38,0:19:47.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fill up the car...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pry my window open...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.59,0:19:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And hold the accelerator in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:20:01.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way, the tires keep spinning\Neven though the car isn't moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:06.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So they can take their time to disarm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.19,0:20:08.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And using a smoke flare and fireworks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:09.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:14.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We made it seem like the car had exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:16.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.37,0:20:19.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you all hadn't followed so closely...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:25.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My brother wouldn't have died...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:29.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your brother wanted to commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.59,0:20:31.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:34.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the reason my brother is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My brother wasn't some suicidal coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:41.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the scene of your brother's accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:43.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was no evidence of the brakes being applied.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, before he crashed into the fence...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had already removed his helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was intentional suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:52.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsumiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:54.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who won't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:59.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you really think what you've done\Nwould make your late brother happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.58,0:21:00.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:02.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsumiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:04.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're lucky, compared to your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, no one died today...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:12.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means you didn't become a murderer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.18,0:21:16.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.72,0:21:19.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you're a lucky guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.43,0:21:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:25.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.37,0:23:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, that kind of surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.12,0:23:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person driving that enormous truck\Nturned out to be Detective Satou.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.92,0:23:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:16.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would you be surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} said you were the one who came up with the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.85,0:23:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.68,0:23:27.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should hurry to the onsen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:29.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to do that now, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.98,0:23:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the half-price special was for today only!
